setBridgeAdapter.t.sol
├── when caller is not the bridge adapter factory
│  └── it should revert with NotFactory
└── when caller has the relevant role
   ├── given an adapter already exists for the provided bridge ID
   │  └── it should revert with BridgeAdapterAlreadyExists
   └── given an adapter does not already exists for the provided bridge ID
      ├── given the provide bridge adapter is the zero address
      │  └── it should revert with ZeroBridgeAdapterAddress
      └── given the provide bridge adapter is not the zero address
         ├── it should assign the provided bridge adapter to the provided bridge ID in controller storage
         ├── it should mark outgoing bridge transfers through the deployed BridgeAdapter as enabled by default
         ├── it should set the max bridge loss basis point value associated with the provided bridge ID to the provided value
         └── it should emit a BridgeAdapterSet event
